<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Gold Donation -- Lushan Novashine Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
Give Lushan Novashine 2gp and receive some experiance and some faction adjustments.<BR>
<BR>
Lushan can be found roaming around North Qeynos, usually between the gates and the "UFO" at the Temple of Life.</div>
<BR>
