<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I made my faction from "apprehensive" to "looks upon you warmly" by doing the Bandit sash quest with a paladin named Chesgard(can't remember his last name). Anyway i works for money too he gives you a bronze weapon or a shield for every sash and you can sell them for about 2pp apiece</font></td></tr></table>
